snippet.title: DOS Game: NetHack - Falcon's Eye
snippet.description:
NetHack - Falcon's Eye intro and gameplay, played and recorded with DOSBox.
Download: https://github.com/zirkoni/Nethack_Falcons_Eye

Finnish game! (The Falcon's Eye interface, not NetHack)

Not sure if you can actually call﻿ this a DOS game because I had to compile the DOS executable myself. I also added some code, sound support for DOS by using the Allegro game programming library.
